Steps to install SASS on Windows:

1. Verified Node.js and npm are installed:
   - Node.js version: v22.17.0
   - npm version: 11.6.1

2. Installed SASS using npm in PowerShell:
   npm install -g sass

3. Verified installation:
   sass --version  # Shows version 1.93.3

4. SASS successfully installed and ready to compile .scss files.